{
  "texts": [
    "On the other hand, novice learners may have difficulty in using AI tools in a way to support their learning, and they may have tendency to use AI tools just to get their assignment done.",
    "Therefore, it can be important to recognize student profiles early in the semester to adopt a pedagogically sounder approach to AI integration to support students from all backgrounds or knowledge levels.",
    "The findings of the study have revealed significant differences in students' post-test scores across different AI interaction profiles.",
    "In the first session, AI-Assisted Code Refiners and AI-Independent Coders outperformed AI-Reliant Code Generators.",
    "This finding suggests that students who engage more actively and critically with AI tools tend to achieve higher performance outcomes."
  ]
}